<text><section>Sec. 2-27. Director—As head; appointment; term.<section>The head of the Personnel Department is the Personnel Director who shall be appointed by the Manager and the Director shall serve at the Manager's will. The Personnel Director shall have had training and experience in personnel administration.</section></section></text><history>(Ord. No. 57-9, § 19.01, 9-3-57; Ord. No. 88-1, § 1, 1-19-88)</history></law>